metadata.title: Skoioje 3Pack Tomato Cage, Easy Assembly Multi-Functional Climbing Vegetables, Plant Stakes and Support Cages Vertical Climbing Plants(Up to 50 inches Tall)
features: 【Multifunctional】Our plant stakes can help the growth of several vertical climbing plants such as eggplant or roses. Prevent plant’s fruit and leaves won’t weigh down the stems.
【Material】 Stainless steel core pile provides sturdy and durable support, will not rust, durable, green thick plastic coating, mixed with plants into a whole, will not affect the beauty.
【Height Adjustable】Three sections superimposed design, free to adjust the height according to the stage of plant growth.
【Multiple Type】You can link them together to form different shapes and heights for the 2 plants you needed them for.
【Easy Assembling】Quickly install and disassemble without tools，At the end of the season they come apart easily and take up very little room for storage.
description: This versatile gardening equipment can also be used for other kinds of fruits and vegetables such as peppers, cucumber, and eggplants. This gardening tool is designed to effectively enclose climbing plants.
This cage takes minimal time and effort to set up. No tools or extra set of hands needed.Convenient to store after dismantling.
Each cage set features 9 assembled 50 inches sturdy stakes made of durable steel for reliable strength.  Durable plastic-coated metal design means long-lasting performance spanning several seasons.
